{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act17side", "eventName": "愚人號", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "SN-ST-9", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "主艦橋", "storyInfo": "蒂亞戈是家園的衛士，他最終向破壞家園的深海教徒露出了獠牙。大審判官苦苦支撐，而斯圖提斐拉號的狩獵亂戰才剛剛開始。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g16_lighthouse_street", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_451_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走快點！", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#4$1"}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃......", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#12$1"}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_451_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這些，溟痕。它們究竟是什麼？", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#9$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "儘管微小，形式不同，但這些螢光的生命也是我們同胞的延展。", "name": "負責拷問的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先知曾說，在海洋的某個部分，發光的生命已經充斥了整個海域。它們即是整體，它們為所有同胞塑造生命的搖籃。", "name": "負責拷問的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“溟痕”......只不過是遙遠的數千數萬海裡外的“祂”隨波而來的些許意志。哪怕只有一丁點，也確確實實在蠶食陸地。", "name": "負責拷問的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "溟痕會將陸地化為另一種海洋。", "name": "負責拷問的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是啊。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊比利亞是你們計畫的第一個犧牲品，格蘭法洛也是。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......！", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#5$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......犧牲品？你是不是，用錯了詞？", "name": "負責拷問的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "審判庭會奪走這座小鎮，看看這些“美麗”的溟痕，它們一樣會。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡不再是我們的家。不再與那段如火的歲月有瓜葛。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂亞戈，你不該——", "name": "負責拷問的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喬迪也被帶走了......那些逃走的人此刻應該都被懲戒軍抓起來了吧。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_451_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們都是兇手。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#7$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "npc_10002", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$Mon3tr_n"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——（激動的尖嘯）", "name": "Mon3tr"}, "figure_art": "npc_10002"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Mon3tr——？！", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#5$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它怎麼會在這裡？！不可能！它明明在城鎮的西邊——！", "name": "負責拷問的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你騙了我們，蒂亞戈！", "name": "負責拷問的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_451_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#7$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有你也是？！", "name": "負責拷問的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......在成為審判庭的臥底之前，我只是一名格蘭法洛工人的女兒。", "name": "冷靜的鎮民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別小看我們的恨意。忍辱負重，只是為了讓你們一同滅亡。", "name": "冷靜的鎮民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_451_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "審判庭也好，你們也好，都只是踐踏了我們家園的敵人。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#7$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_451_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來看看毀滅的模樣吧，看看我們當年所看見的。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#7$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂亞戈——！躲開！", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#7$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_451_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔！", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#6$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Character", "attri